data.description: Exceptional Boardman Colonial featuring an inviting living room with a cozy fireplace, a formal dining room adorned with beautiful hardwood floors, and a kitchen for culinary enthusiasts. The rear family room addition adds extra space for relaxation, complemented by the convenience of an attached 2 car garage. A divided partially finished basement provides versatility, with another functioning fireplace. Moving on to four spacious bedrooms with a master having cedar closets and ample storage in each bedroom.  Freshly painted throughout and tastefully decorated for you to move right in! Additional walk up attic space could be transitioned into additional living space. Basement has been professionally waterproofed with KRON, "life of the home guarantee" Furnace 2020 and A/C 2021, newly landscaped and so much more!  America's Preferred Home Warranty offered.
